Package Description
es.utils.doublekeymap
Provides the classes necessary to handle a map having two keys.
es.utils.mapper
Provides a all the code of the mapping.
es.utils.mapper.annotation
Provides the annotation that can be used to configure the mappings operations directly from the Object class.
es.utils.mapper.configuration
Provides a class for the configuration af the Mapper.
es.utils.mapper.converter
Provides a generic AbstractConverter class that is need to be extended to create custom converters between types.
es.utils.mapper.defaultvalue
Provides a generic DefaultValueFactory class that is need to be extended to create custom supplier for default value.
es.utils.mapper.exception
Provides the exception that can be thrown during the execution o the code.
es.utils.mapper.factory
Provides a factory class to help the user to create custom mappings.
es.utils.mapper.factory.builder
Provides a a Step builder implementation for creating a ElementMapper step by step.
es.utils.mapper.holder
Provides a class that contains the information of a field used in the mappings.
es.utils.mapper.impl
Provides a class handling the mapping between two different types.
es.utils.mapper.impl.element
Provides a class handling the mapping of a single element of a class.
es.utils.mapper.impl.object
Provides a class handling the mapping between two different types.
es.utils.mapper.utils
Provides a set of utility classes useful in the implementation.
